// About page component import React from 'react'; const About = () => { return (

🏥 About MediScan-AI

Revolutionizing healthcare with artificial intelligence

🎯 Our Mission

MediScan-AI is dedicated to making advanced medical diagnosis tools accessible to everyone. We leverage cutting-edge artificial intelligence to provide instant, accurate analysis of medical images and symptoms, helping bridge the gap between patients and healthcare professionals.

🔬 Technology Stack

🤖 AI Models

  • Skin Cancer Detection: ISIC-trained ResNet-50
  • Chest X-ray Analysis: CheXNet DenseNet-121
  • Virtual Triage: Groq + Tavily + Keyword AI

🖥️ Frontend

  • React.js with modern hooks
  • Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
  • Real-time chat interface
  • Progressive Web App features

⚙️ Backend

  • FastAPI for high-performance APIs
  • PyTorch for deep learning inference
  • Docker containerization
  • Comprehensive logging and monitoring

🌟 Key Features

🔬

Skin Lesion Analysis

Advanced computer vision models trained on the ISIC dataset can identify various skin conditions including melanoma, basal cell carcinoma, and benign lesions with high accuracy.

  • 7 different skin condition classifications
  • Confidence scoring and risk assessment
  • Lesion characteristic analysis
  • Personalized recommendations
🩻

Chest X-ray Analysis

CheXNet-based models can detect 14 different pathologies in chest X-rays, providing rapid screening and triage capabilities for healthcare providers.

  • 14 pathology classifications
  • Multi-label detection capabilities
  • Urgency level assessment
  • Clinical findings generation
🩺

Virtual Triage Assistant

Intelligent chatbot powered by advanced language models that can assess symptoms, provide guidance, and determine appropriate levels of care.

  • Natural language symptom assessment
  • Urgency level determination
  • Personalized recommendations
  • Integration with medical knowledge bases

🔒 Privacy & Security

🛡️ Data Protection

All medical images and data are processed securely and are not stored on our servers without explicit user consent.

🔐 Encryption

End-to-end encryption ensures that your sensitive medical information remains private and secure during transmission.

📋 Compliance

Built with HIPAA compliance in mind, following best practices for medical data handling and privacy protection.

⚠️ Important Disclaimers

Medical Disclaimer

MediScan-AI is designed as a diagnostic assistance tool and should not replace professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult with qualified healthcare professionals for medical concerns.

Accuracy Limitations

While our AI models are trained on extensive medical datasets and achieve high accuracy rates, they are not infallible. Results should always be interpreted by medical professionals.

Emergency Situations

In case of medical emergencies, do not rely on this application. Call emergency services (911) immediately for urgent medical situations.

👥 Our Team

MediScan-AI is developed by a team of experienced software engineers, data scientists, and medical professionals committed to improving healthcare accessibility through technology.

5+
Years of AI Research
100K+
Medical Images Analyzed
95%+
Accuracy Rate

📞 Contact & Support

📧 General Inquiries

info@mediscan-ai.com

🛠️ Technical Support

support@mediscan-ai.com

🏥 Medical Partnerships

partnerships@mediscan-ai.com

📱 Follow Us

Twitter LinkedIn GitHub

🚀 Future Roadmap

Q2 2024

  • Mobile app development
  • Additional imaging modalities (MRI, CT)
  • Multi-language support

Q3 2024

  • Integration with EHR systems
  • Telemedicine platform integration
  • Advanced reporting features

Q4 2024

  • AI model improvements
  • Real-time collaboration tools
  • API for third-party integrations
); }; export default About;
